title: [1508521049] Beef Wellington, Prison Style - Gordon Behind Bars
description:
To showcase his new prison brigade, Gordon organises a meal in the prison for 50 influential players in the industry. Can the prisoners master this classic Ramsay dish?

Subscribe for weekly cooking videos.
